Package imagingbook Description

This package contains the common library used by the ImageJ plugins provided for Digital Image Processing books authored by Wilhelm Burger and Mark J Burge, published by Springer. See also http://www.imagingbook.com and https://sourceforge.net/projects/imagingbook/.

Permission to use and distribute this software is granted under the BSD 2-Clause "Simplified" License (see http://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-2-Clause). Copyright (c) 2006-2015 Wilhelm Burger, Mark J. Burge. All rights reserved.

Requires Java 1.5 or higher.

Author:
Wilhelm Burger and Mark J. Burge
